config XIAOMI_MIEV
	tristate "Xiaomi MIEV exception event transport"
	help
	  Build the Xiaomi MIEV exception/event transport module.
	  The driver creates /dev/miev and exports the cdev_tevent_* helper
	  ABI used by Xiaomi vendor modules to submit structured diagnostic
	  events.
	  Exported symbols:
	    cdev_tevent_alloc
	    cdev_tevent_add_int
	    cdev_tevent_add_str
	    cdev_tevent_write
	    cdev_tevent_destroy
	  If unsure, say M when building Xiaomi vendor touch/thermal modules
	  that depend on miev.ko.
